menu "Knot peer discovery"

config KNOT_ENABLED
    bool "Enable knot peer-discovery table"
    default WEBUI_MINING_UI
    help
      Compile in the knot component: mDNS browse, peer table (g_peer_table[32]),
      and the /api/knot route. Enabled by default when the mining web UI is on
      (WEBUI_MINING_UI=y) and disabled on headless boards where the dashboard is
      not served. The ~8.3 KB .bss peer table and associated code are removed from
      the binary when this is off.

      Knot is informational-only (feeds /api/knot for the dashboard dashboard) and
      has no impact on mining, stratum, WiFi, or OTA.

endmenu
